    "body": "The unit test:\r\n```\r\nlib/spack/spack/test/llnl/util/tty/log.py::test_foreground_background_output\r\n```\r\ngives a fair amount of false positives on Github (failures of the test that are not due to a regression). \r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\nLook at failing PRs, there are high chances the failure log looks like [this one](https://github.com/spack/spack/pull/18739/checks?check_run_id=1272787694).\r\n\r\n\r\n### Error Message\r\n--\r\n\r\n### Information on your system\r\n--\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\nMaintainers can retry the test suite by restarting it manually, or users can:\r\n1. Close/reopen the PR \r\n2. Rebase the PR\r\n\r\nto trigger tests again.\r\n\r\n- [x] I have searched the issues of this repo and believe this is not a duplicate\r\n",
